<HL>
   Wednesday's Markets:
   Bonds Fall
   On Fears
   Of Unflation
   ---
   CPI Report Is Cited;
   Stocks Drop 18.07
   As Dollar Is Mixed
   ----
   By Christopher Winans
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
